  <brief_title>Increasing Viral Testing in the Emergency Department</brief_title>
  <acronym>InVITED</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 2/3 Clinical Trial of the Effect of a Brief Intervention on Uptake of Rapid Testing for HIV and Hepatitis C Among Emergency Department Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
